================================================================================
DATA — Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
================================================================================

Applies to the derived datasets in site/src/data/ (rankings.json, openness.json,
matrix.json, weights.json) and to any copy of them published under /data/.

These files are derived in part from World Bank World Development Indicators and
UN DESA international migrant stock data, themselves released under CC BY 4.0.
The derived work is licensed on the same terms so the attribution chain holds.

You are free to share and adapt the data for any purpose, including
commercially, provided you give appropriate credit, link to the license, and
indicate if changes were made.

